  <brief_title>The Rate of C-reactive Protein (CRP) Increase as a Marker for Bacterial Infections in Children</brief_title>
  <acronym>CRPv</acronym>
  <official_title>CRP Velocity as a Marker for Bacterial Infections in Children</official_title>
